headline.print_headline: Van Gaal Names Final World Cup Squad
headline.main: Van Gaal Names Final World Cup Squad

lead_paragraph: Louis van Gaal named a mix of experience and youth in his final 23-man World Cup squad Saturday, as the Netherlands seeks to go one better than its runner-up finish in 2010.
